TABLE I â€“ CORRELATING THE 2022 VERSION TO THE 2017 VERSION OF THE HARMONIZED SYSTEM November 2020 2022 Version 2017 Version Remarks 0208.90 ex 0208.90 Amendment of the scope of subheading 0208.90 as a result of the separate identification of edible, non-living insects in new subheading 0410.10.
